text: The European Institute of Education (eie) is a government licensed institute of further and higher education in San Ġwann, Malta. The institute was established in 2000. Student recruitment offices operate in various European and Asian cities. It provides Malta Government Scholarship Scheme to its Students. EIE conducts various Courses in Business and Management at Academic Level and also Executive courses Executive Education. A collaboration agreement has been signed between the European Institute of Education and the Young Entrepreneurs and Leaders Organisation (YEL). ==Notes== Category:Schools in Malta Category:San Ġwann
title: European Institute of Education
